OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FA group of cross-party councillors are
OL,7,Furging the Government to block plans
OL,8,Fto close a children's accident and
OL,9,Femergency unit.
OL,11,FMembers of Lancashire County Council's
OL,12,Fhealth scrutiny committee have written
OL,13,Fto the Health and Social Care
OL,14,FSecretary Wes Streeting to express
OL,15,Ftheir concerns over the plans, which
OL,16,Fwould see Ormskirk Hospital's
OL,17,Fchildren's A&E services move to
OL,18,FSouthport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FHealth leaders say the eight-mile move
OL,7,Fis the only way to provide round-the-
OL,8,Fclock emergency care for youngsters in
OL,9,FWest Lancashire and Sefton, but the
OL,10,Fdecision was met with backlash from
OL,11,Flocals.
OL,13,FThe committee, made up of County and
OL,14,FDistrict Councillors, has now formally
OL,15,Frequested that Mr Streeting "calls in"
OL,16,Fthe plans to consider them for himself
OL,17,Fand potentially reverse the change.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FThe group unanimously backed the move
OL,7,Fseeking his intervention on 30 March.
OL,8,FMembers cited concerns over the
OL,9,Fprocess surrounding the NHS decision
OL,10,Fand questioned whether the shake-up
OL,11,Fwas in "the best interests" of health
OL,12,Fservices in West Lancashire.
OL,14,FThe relocation plan ` which will
OL,15,Fcreate a single 24-hour A&E service
OL,16,Ffor adults and children in Southport `
OL,17,Fwas approved by a joint committee of
OL,18,Fthe NHS integrated care boards (ICBs)
OL,19,Ffor Lancashire and South Cumbria, and
OL,20,FCheshire and Merseyside on 13 March.
OL,26,@sD@HOUsD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FCounty Cllr Shaun Crimmins condemned
OL,7,Fthe fact that a "preferred option" `
OL,8,Fto move the children's A&E to
OL,9,FSouthport, as opposed to the adult
OL,10,Femergency unit to Ormskirk ` had been
OL,11,Fset out by health officials before a
OL,12,Fpublic consultation.
OL,14,FHe told the meeting, attended by the
OL,15,FLocal Democracy Service: "A lot of
OL,16,Fpeople disengaged from (the)
OL,17,Fconsultation, because they said it was
OL,18,Fa done deal."
OL,26,@oD@QOUoD@bO]wD@ZOUxD@XpmxD@\pnzD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FCounty Cllr Gaynor Hargreaves also
OL,7,Fraised concerns over the potential
OL,8,Fdelays in children receiving emergency
OL,9,Fcare due to the extra travel time for
OL,10,FWest Lancashire residents.
OL,12,F"Those few minutes could make a
OL,13,Fdifference to life and death," she
OL,14,Fsaid, adding that she did not feel the
OL,15,Fmatter had been "addressed in full,
OL,16,Flike it should be".
OL,26,@uD@^O]wD@QOUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FThe issue of transport between West
OL,7,FLancashire and Southport was also
OL,8,Fraised, with County Cllr Mark Jewell
OL,9,Ftelling the meeting that the
OL,10,F"mitigations" promised by the NHS as
OL,11,Fpart of the overhaul were not
OL,12,F"obvious".
OL,14,FMeanwhile, committee member Cllr Ann
OL,15,FFennell ` who sits on West Lancashire
OL,16,FBorough Council ` said the change
OL,17,Fcould to lead to Ormskirk also losing
OL,18,Fmaternity services in future.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@MO]tD@AOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FLancashire County Council's health
OL,7,Fscrutiny committee will now set out
OL,8,Fthe reasons for their call-in request
OL,9,Fin a letter to the health secretary.
OL,11,FBut government guidance on the
OL,12,Fprocedure stresses that the power is
OL,13,Fnot expected to be used "on a regular
OL,14,Fbasis".
OL,16,FBefore a request is accepted, NHS
OL,17,Fcommissioning bodies and local
OL,18,Fauthorities should have taken "all
OL,19,Freasonable steps to try to resolve any
OL,20,Fissues".
OL,26,@uD@YOUvD@FO]zD@_OU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FWest Lancashire MP Ashley Dalton said
OL,7,Fon the day of the ICBs' decision that
OL,8,Fshe would make her own call-in bid
OL,9,Fover the issue.
OL,11,FThe prospects of either having an all-
OL,12,Fage service on both sites or
OL,13,Fmaintaining the status quo were both
OL,14,Fruled out prior to the survey
OL,15,Fbeginning, having been deemed
OL,16,Funsustainable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FThe ICBs say that the involvement of
OL,7,Fmore than 7,800 people with the
OL,8,Fconsultation equated to just over 3%
OL,9,Fof the local population, well above
OL,10,Fthe national average response rate of
OL,11,F0.7%.
OL,13,FRespondents generally wanted services
OL,14,Flocated closer to where they lived.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FIn a joint statement responding to the
OL,7,Fcommittee's call-in request, the
OL,8,FLancashire and South Cumbria and
OL,9,FCheshire and Merseyside ICBs said: "We
OL,10,Fnote the decision taken by Lancashire
OL,11,FCounty Council's health and adult
OL,12,Fservices scrutiny committee.
OL,14,F"The joint committee of the two ICBs
OL,15,Fmade the decision to co-locate adult
OL,16,Fand children's A&E at Southport
OL,17,FHospital based on the public
OL,18,Fconsultation findings alongside
OL,19,Fclinical, financial, equalities,
OL,20,Fworkforce and quality evidence.
OL,26,@qD@dOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,F"The decision was about making sure we
OL,7,Fhave a 24/7 emergency department for
OL,8,Fboth adults and children at the same
OL,9,Fsite which will safely and sustainably
OL,10,Fdeliver emergency care for people
OL,11,Fliving in Southport, Formby and West
OL,12,FLancashire.
OL,14,F"It is important to note Ormskirk
OL,15,FHospital will remain open and continue
OL,16,Fto provide key services to patients,
OL,17,Fincluding outpatient services, urgent
OL,18,Ftreatment, planned care, diagnostics,
OL,19,Fand inpatient services.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,F"There is active investment planned
OL,7,Ffor the site and it's vital to
OL,8,Fremember that currently 86 percent of
OL,9,Factivity is not A&E."
OL,11,FThe young people's A&E at Ormskirk and
OL,12,FDistrict General Hospital currently
OL,13,Fcloses between midnight and 8am, and
OL,14,Fthere has been no emergency unit for
OL,15,Fchildren at Southport and Formby
OL,16,FDistrict General Hospital since 2002.
OL,26,@qD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FThe transfer of the children's A&E to
OL,7,FSouthport was also described as being
OL,8,F"substantially more affordable" than
OL,9,Fmoving the adult service to Ormskirk `
OL,10,Fwith estimated capital costs for the
OL,11,Ftwo schemes of #33.1m and #91.3m,
OL,12,Frespectively.
OL,14,FThe NHS says the switch to Southport
OL,15,Ffor children means only one "co-
OL,16,Fdependent service" ` the paediatric
OL,17,Finpatient unit - also has to move.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@_O]wD@]OUxD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774973462
OL,3,CCouncillors call on Government to
OL,4,Cblock children's A&E move
OL,6,FHowever, if the adult A&E were
OL,7,Frelocated to Ormskirk, seven co-
OL,8,Fdependent services would have to go
OL,9,Fwith it - general medicine, critical
OL,10,Fcare, elderly medicine, respiratory
OL,11,Fmedicine, medical gastroenterology,
OL,12,Fpathology and liaison psychiatry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/14
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
